Assets.Name: Meshallah+
Assets.Description:
Meshallah+ v0.0.1

I basically am working on this for some days now almost all the time and I wanted to share my first versio ... n I feel comfortable sharing with others. My plan is to finish the outdoor park and add some street skating areas around it. For now the hall and outdoor park are working. Still missing are trees and grass in the designated areas + some props. The inddor location will may be extended one day. Nothing on the obstacles is fixed so changes might come. For now everything is skateable.

Working for now are:
* Day and night cycle
* Radio
* Collisions
* Phys Materials

Some work needed on:
* UV Maps
* Lighting
* Placement

It's not much for now but maybe some people will enjoy it :P

PS: Some times might make the outdoors a bit weird (couldnt see the rail properly at 9am) so test around a bit
